# Project: hcc-admin-v2 (Frontend)

## Stack
- Next.js App Router, React 19, JavaScript only (NO TypeScript)
- State: Zustand with sessionStorage persist (src/store/store.js)
- UI: Tailwind CSS + SCSS + MUI + Radix UI
- Editors: Tiptap (rich text), Excalidraw (whiteboard)

## Data Fetching Patterns (THREE coexist — match the file you're in)
- **GraphQL/Apollo**: contacts domain only (src/graphql/contactQueries.js, contactMutations.js)
- **SWR + dedicated service/hook**: Notes module only (src/services/noteApi.js, src/hooks/useNotes.js, src/hooks/useMentions.js)
- **Direct axios + apiPath**: all other modules — call REST APIs directly inside components

## API URL Pattern
- Legacy modules use `apiPath.prodPath` from `src/utils/routes.js` — KEEP THIS in files that already use it
- Newer utils use `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` from `.env`
- NEVER migrate URL patterns mid-feature — match what the file already uses

## Auth
- Login API call: `src/app/(auth)/login/page.js`
- Auth state management: `src/store/store.js`
- URL constants: `src/utils/routes.js` (primary), `src/utils/apiRoutes.js` (secondary)
- Auth is client-side redirect only — no middleware.ts route protection exists

## Key Directories
- Pages: `src/app/(pages)/`
- Reusable UI: `src/components/ui/`
- Feature components: `src/components/subcomponents/`
- Drawers: `src/components/subcomponents/drawers/`
- Tables: `src/components/subcomponents/tables/`